	(text_box "NOTES:\n\nATTiny416:\n- i2c must be at 3v3\n- should store chunk ID\n- convert i2c -> DRV8834 inputs\n\nDRV8834:\n- stepper motor driver\n- 2.5-10.8v input\n\nMPM3610AGQV-P:\n- Handles all expected batt ranges in (0.8 - 18.2V)\n- Converts to 3v3 out (driven by ____ resistor value)\n- (1.2A continuous)"
